- "Constellation of consumer satisfaction" is a metaphor for the collection of highly-rated products;
- "Total revenue" is the sum of the item prices multiplied by the quantity sold for each product;
- "Total savings customers have enjoyed through coupon use" is the sum of the total savings calculated for each user who used coupons.

